<td align="center"><b>
<i>Svastra compta</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Melissodes compta </i>Cresson, 1878; Anthedon_homonym compta &#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;; <i>Anthedonia compta </i>&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;</small><p>
