&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apidae">Apidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Svastra">Svastra</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Anthedonia&name=Svastra&flags=subgenus:"><i>Anthedonia</i></a></small>
